BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Journey to Mars: Another Giant Leap for Mankind 3D / Cesta na Mars
 : Další velký skok pro lidstvo 3D
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Prague:20260424T180000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Prague:20260424T185500
DTSTAMP:20260421T040651Z
UID:5152d99867c8307e@cal-scraper
DESCRIPTION:One small step was just the beginning. Now we venture further 
 – driven by unquenchable curiosity\, with our eyes set on Mars and the d
 etermination to write the boldest chapter of human exploration.\nSuitable 
 from age 10\nEnglish audio available. The show is simultaneously projected
  with English audio in headphones. It may\, however\, contain a live part 
 presented exclusively in Czech. Headphones are available on request at the
  ticket desk. The deposit for headphones is 100 CZK per piece (cash only).
 \n3D stereoscopic show\nTickets: https://www.brnoid.cz/cs/hvezdarna-vstupe
 nky?e=32213\n\n⚠️ Unofficial source – verify details on the organize
 r's website. Auto-translated via Azure OpenAI.\n\n---\n\nPrice/Cena: cena:
  200/150\nDatum: 24/4/2026\, 18:00\n\n---\n\nJeden malý krok byl pouhým 
 začátkem. Teď se vydáváme ještě dál – vedeni neuhasitelnou zvěd
 avostí\, s pohledem upřeným k Marsu a s odhodláním napsat nejodvážn
 ější kapitolu lidského putování\nvhodné od 10 let\nEnglish audio av
 ailableThe show is simultaneously projected with English audio in headphon
 es. It may\, however\, contain a live part presented in Czech language exc
 lusively. Headphones are available on request at the ticket desk. The depo
 sit for headphones is 100 CZK per piece (cash only).\n3D stereoskopický p
 ořad\nVstupenky: https://www.brnoid.cz/cs/hvezdarna-vstupenky?e=32213\n\n
 ⚠️ Neoficiální zdroj – ověřte si detaily na webu pořadatele.
LOCATION:digitárium - veřejnost
URL:https://www.hvezdarna.cz/porad/cesta-na-mars-dalsi-velky-skok-pro-lids
 tvo-3d/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Universe Through All Senses 3D / Vesmír všemi smysly 3D
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Prague:20260424T200000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Prague:20260424T205500
DTSTAMP:20260421T040651Z
UID:ce89ce454e3bcf8f@cal-scraper
DESCRIPTION:Experience the universe through all your senses! You will lear
 n what it’s like to touch the universe\, how a comet or outer space smel
 ls\, and what flavor Saturn's moon Enceladus or Mars has. And to make it e
 ven more special\, we’ll provide you with special 3D glasses that will e
 nhance the experience.\nSuitable from age 12\nEnglish audio available. The
  show is simultaneously projected with English audio in headphones. It may
 \, however\, contain a live part presented exclusively in Czech. Headphone
 s are available on request at the ticket desk. The deposit for headphones 
 is 100 CZK per piece (cash only).\n3D stereoscopic show\nTickets: https://
 www.brnoid.cz/cs/hvezdarna-vstupenky?e=32214\n\n⚠️ Unofficial source 
 – verify details on the organizer's website. Auto-translated via Azure O
 penAI.\n\n---\n\nPrice/Cena: cena: 200/150\nDatum: 24/4/2026\, 20:00\n\n--
 -\n\nPoznejte vesmír všemi smysly! Dozvíte se\, jaké to je dotýkat se
  vesmíru\, jak voní kometa či kosmický prostor i jakou příchuť má 
 Saturnův měsíc Enceladus nebo planeta Mars. A aby toho nebylo málo\, n
 asadíme vám k tomu speciální 3D brýle\, které celkový zážitek je
 ště umocní.\nvhodné od 12 let\nEnglish audio availableThe show is simu
 ltaneously projected with English audio in headphones. It may\, however\, 
 contain a live part presented in Czech language exclusively. Headphones ar
 e available on request at the ticket desk. The deposit for headphones is 1
 00 CZK per piece (cash only).\n3D stereoskopický pořad\nVstupenky: https
 ://www.brnoid.cz/cs/hvezdarna-vstupenky?e=32214\n\n⚠️ Neoficiální zd
 roj – ověřte si detaily na webu pořadatele.
LOCATION:digitárium - veřejnost
URL:https://www.hvezdarna.cz/porad/vesmir-vsemi-smysly-3d/
