 těm nejmenším kosmonautům.\nvhodné od 5 let\nEnglish audio availableT
 he show is simultaneously projected with English audio in headphones. It m
 ay\, however\, contain a live part presented in Czech language exclusively
 . Headphones are available on request at the ticket desk. The deposit for 
