DESCRIPTION:Imagine a future where there are no humans left – only cats 
 remain. But not the ones lounging on the couch. These have spacesuits\, sh
 uttles\, and plenty of courage! Kiki\, Tutti\, and Pepe – catnauts – h
 ave a mission that sounds quite ordinary: to clean up space debris. Howeve
 r\, when you acquire a Galactic Broom (yes\, a shuttle that sweeps)\, it
 ’s never just about cleaning. This and much more is the subject of the l
 atest show\, Cat Adventure During the Super Full Moon\, aimed at the young
 est little astronauts.\nSuitable from age 5\nEnglish audio available. The 
 show is simultaneously projected with English audio in headphones. It may\
 , however\, contain a live part presented exclusively in Czech. Headphones
  are available on request at the ticket desk. The deposit for headphones i
 s 100 CZK per piece (cash only).\nTickets: https://www.brnoid.cz/cs/hvezda
 rna-vstupenky?e=32361\n\n⚠️ Unofficial source – verify details on th
